The Redeemed Christian Church of God (RCCG), Latter House Assembly will Hold its Mothering Sunday on March 27. The event, according to the church, would be held at the RCCG Latter House Assembly Area headquarters, Lagos Province 2. The programme tagged, ‘Blessed Among Women’, would hold at 1b Agbedina Avenue, Olowora Junction, behind Sweet Sensation, Berger in Isheri, Isheri local council, Lagos. Ministering would be Pastor Ifeanyi Chukwu Nweke and other ministers of God.